{"tid":2097191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普短期內或公布對華行動，涉及中國、製造業、移民及處方藥物價格。","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T17:20:26.000Z","uid":189046,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"58a44f82f68424e523c4baeb7450857daf7dd8da","tid":2097191,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"特朗普短期內或公布對華行動<br />\n<br />\n外電引述白宮幕僚長梅多斯（Mark Meadows）表示，美國總統特朗普正準備就一系列行政命令，範疇涉及中國、製造業、移民及處方藥物價格。<br />\n<br />\n梅多斯又指，正在研究如何確保解決中國問題，如何將製造業從海外帶回美國，以確保美國工人就業，亦將研究與移民有關問題及處方藥價格。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200706/B5LASUJHDYH6LZTT274SO6QLY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200706%2FB5LASUJHDYH6LZTT274SO6QLY4%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=494cbe9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200706%2FB5LASUJHDYH6LZTT274SO6QLY4%2F&h=d43f1e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200706/B5LASUJHDYH6LZTT274SO6QLY4/</a>"},{"pid":"b6833cb902f602b31178a9f1bebcb07ba459a6ad","tid":2097191,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"